        <mxCell id="fAf-Ev9ntNy3SwEQ4uAw-1" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;" value="&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;. Ride Booking System – Book a Ride&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&#xa;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top:0in&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;&#xa; &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in&quot;&gt;The&#xa;     user enters pickup and destination locations.&lt;/li&gt;&#xa; &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in&quot;&gt;The&#xa;     system displays available drivers and fare estimates.&lt;/li&gt;&#xa; &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in&quot;&gt;The&#xa;     user selects a ride and confirms the booking.&lt;/li&gt;&#xa; &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in&quot;&gt;The&#xa;     system assigns a driver to the user.&lt;/li&gt;&#xa; &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in&quot;&gt;The&#xa;     system notifies both the driver and the user.&lt;/li&gt;&#xa; &lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .5in&quot;&gt;The&#xa;     ride is tracked until completion.&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
